{"tid":868720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[6月29]建造業對人才需求大，年輕人要好好裝備自己，把握機遇","createTime":"2018-10-19T17:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T05:15:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f9a6f6710ddcb1ae141df39758acc2375634c24e","tid":868720,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"建造業對人才需求大，業界<span style=\"color: red;\">年輕人要好好裝備自己，把握機遇</span>，參加技能比賽是其中一個好方法。香港建造業議會（下稱「議會」）日前舉辦「香港建造業青年技能大賽」，設砌磚、細木等6個比賽項目，由行內「老行尊」擔任評審。參賽者都凝神屏氣，在各個項目一較高下，當中最年輕的參賽者只有16歲，更勇奪項目冠軍，令人驚喜！<br />\n<br />\n議會執行總監鄭定寕指，<span style=\"color: red;\">不少年輕人有感建造業發展前景良好，有意加入</span>，未來議會將提供更多培訓課程，及舉辦更多活動提升他們的專業技能。有經驗的師傅則可傳授工藝予年輕人，驅使建造業逐步邁向專業化和科技化，為建造業增添新血。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180629083334\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180629083334&h=6471a74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180629%2Fbkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html&d=wFyamN%2FazAoqefmseq8hy26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=82ee4904\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"988823f1f2780b6c230d14aaf2cc490d756f1ece","tid":868720,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"★建造業前期工種開工不足　紮鐵模板面臨凍薪<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bHjDMS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bHjDMS</a>"},{"pid":"5bbcaa5b15e0844e26c91695e0209b8a36a3ab9f","tid":868720,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:23:03.000Z","msg":"腦魔咁夜仲唔訓"},{"pid":"33151f7a981e8987832